cars.name: MERCEDES BENZ E450 Cabrio
cars.description: A powerful and efficient 2.0L inline-4 turbocharged engine. It delivers 221 horsepower at 5500 rpm and 258 lb-ft of torque at 1800 rpm, providing smooth and responsive acceleration.

cars.name: MERCEDES BENZ GLA 220D AMG Line
cars.description: The embodiment of luxury and sophistication in the form of a convertible. With a powerful V6 biturbo engine, this car combines performance with refinement. Its exterior design is elegant and aerodynamic. The retractable top opens in seconds, offering the freedom to enjoy the sun and wind. Whether exploring the city or cruising highways, it offers an exceptionally gratifying experience.

cars.name: ASTON MARTIN DBX 707
cars.description: Redefines the concept of luxury SUV with its combination of exceptional performance and timeless elegance. Powered by a 4.0-liter V8 biturbo engine, this vehicle offers impressive power and agile handling both on and off the road. Its aerodynamic design reflects Aston Martin's craftsmanship. Inside, luxury blends with technology to create a sublime driving environment.

cars.name: MCLAREN 765LT
cars.description: Fuses cutting-edge technology with masterful engineering. With its 4.0-liter twin-turbo V8 engine, this supercar delivers unmatched power and impressive acceleration that pushes the limits of possibility. Its aerodynamically inspired design, born from competition, ensures optimal performance while projecting an imposing presence on the road. Every curve and straightaway becomes an unforgettable experience.
